Soldiers Loot Shops in Southern Burkina Faso, Reuters Reports

-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 
2011-04-18T05:47:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-18/soldiers-loot-shops-in-southern-burkina-faso-reuters-reports.html
Soldiers looted shops and stole
cars yesterday in the southern  Burkina Faso  town of Po as part
of a protest over pay, Reuters reported, citing residents of the
town.   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  